.modal-header
  h4.modal-title
    i.fas.fa-puzzle-piece.me-2
    | Extension Recommendation
  button.btn-close((click)="dismiss()")

.modal-body
  p
    | For a more seamless experience, we recommend installing the 
    strong Tabby Copilot Opener
    |  extension from the VS Code Marketplace.
  
  .d-flex.justify-content-center.my-3
    button.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg((click)="openMarketplace()")
      i.fas.fa-store.me-2
      | View in Marketplace

  small.text-muted
    | This extension allows Tabby to directly communicate with VS Code, enabling faster and more reliable opening of the Copilot window.

.modal-footer
  button.btn.btn-secondary((click)="dismiss()")
    | Dismiss